==Description==
The '''Splash Plate''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]]. They can then be sold for 100 Water [[Gems]][[File:Water_Gem.png|15px]] or traded for other items in Daily Deals if available that day.

==Details==
The Splash Plate has a value of 100 [[Gems|Water Gems]] {{Gem|Water}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals.

==Acquisition==
Splash Plates can be found in the [[Underground]], traded for with the [[Berry Master|Hoenn Berry Master]], and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

